Class Submission

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.dean.jraw.models.JsonModel
      • net.dean.jraw.models.RedditObject
        • net.dean.jraw.models.Thing
          • net.dean.jraw.models.Contribution

              • net.dean.jraw.models.Submission
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Created, Distinguishable, Gildable, JsonAttribute, Votable

    @Model(kind=LINK,
       serializer=SubmissionSerializer.class,
       validate=false)
public final class Submission
extends PublicContribution
    Represents content that the user has submitted, whether that be a self post or a link. More information can be found here.

        @JsonProperty
public Submission.ThumbnailType getThumbnailType()
